{
  "stem": "5496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, you have to forget.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's gone with you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Your new life is starting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She would always bring out different details, but it was suppressed and people really didn't want to hear.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I never volunteered to talk to anyone about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They already knew of, course, that I'm a survivor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I never hid it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so we spoke about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never had nightmares, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There isn't, as I said, a day or a moment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to this day I can't look at a chimney.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to move from somewhere because there was a chimney.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And things like that, of course, that just automatically-- the human mind plays funny tricks on you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They remind you of things even when you don't want to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, of course, my day starts with a prayer for my martyred family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There's just one incident, if I may say, which will always be in my heart.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Aunt Rose took it upon herself after the war to go to Auschwitz where she took some earth, since we don't have a grave at all for my family.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she took it to Budapest where her father, who happened to be by chance at the time when he collapsed and died of a heart attack, is buried.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she made a memorial on the grave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it's became my [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Fred and I see to it that it's being taken care of.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And whenever we are in Europe, we go there personally to see that, indeed, it's in order, since that's the only remaining monument to our martyred family.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let's see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My English, hopefully it's of any-- any good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I speak German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I manage in German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I speak Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I speak Czech and Slovak.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
